title: Raymundo’s SHOCKING Country Music Secrets + Dylan Scott Performs His Hits! + Fun Fact Friday: Amy Gets Challenged By A Listener!
itunes:title: Raymundo’s SHOCKING Country Music Secrets + Dylan Scott Performs His Hits! + Fun Fact Friday: Amy Gets Challenged By A Listener!
description:
Raymundo reveals some shocking country music secrets and Bobby and the crew determine whether we think there is any truth to them. Dylan Scott stops by and talks about the jobs he had before becoming an artist and performs a couple of his hits for us! Amy takes on a listener who called in claiming he could out fun fact her…we find out if he is a worthy challenger!
